{"id":600265583,"lang":"java","time":"1 week, 3 days","timestamp":1639236008,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"5 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/600265583/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Edit Distance","memory":"39.3 MB","code":"class Solution {\n    public int minDistance(String word1, String word2) {\n        int m = word1.length();\n        int n = word2.length();\n        \n        int dist[][] = new int[m+1][n+1];\n        \n        \n        for(int i=0;i<m+1;i++){\n            for(int j=0;j<n+1;j++){\n                if(i==0) dist[i][j] = j;\n                if(j==0) dist[i][j] = i;\n            }\n        }\n        \n        for(int i=1;i<m+1;i++){\n            for(int j=1;j<n+1;j++){\n                if(word1.charAt(i-1) == word2.charAt(j-1)){\n                    dist[i][j] = dist[i-1][j-1];\n                }else{\n                    dist[i][j] = 1 + Math.min(dist[i-1][j],Math.min( dist[i][j-1], dist[i-1][j-1] ));\n                }\n            }\n        }\n        \n        return dist[m][n];\n        \n        \n    }\n}","compare_result":"","title_slug":"edit-distance"}
